    "text_body": "\r\n \r\n \r\n\r\n \r\nhttps://click.my.jobs.ch/?qs=ABB7InYiOjEsImQiOjQ4OTl9AAEAAAAAAKYlv4KdoA6q9riqNbnfDIdE3MY401uEdh5nT0DuompUOhabKrig8Y9OutFSvFjyUWjt3NVZIoyVqMVeMn8FNDTNuBrRgUpStngrPy2WGW9T \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n Hello,\r\n\r\n\r\n You've taken the first step by creating your jobup.ch account. Now, let's go further together!\r\n\r\n\r\n Have you explored all the benefits available through your account? Here&rsquo;s a quick look at some of the features waiting for you in your personal space. Discover them now!\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&#128276; \r\nhttps://click.my.jobs.ch/?qs=ABB7InYiOjEsImQiOjQ4OTl9AAEAAAAAAKYlv4KeBpU8CSevdjU7FsdnUypLLhCK1hIrb7aIJ3CnJQ1i2YRI_FWr1t8bjEKZ9P0mO-3pZ2AgDbL0vqQ5DRT1PWJoNi1SKVP4TU9qmDKF \r\nSet up a job alert  based on what you&rsquo;re looking for and receive new job offers directly in your inbox.\r\n&#128204; \r\nhttps://click.my.jobs.ch/?qs=ABB7InYiOjEsImQiOjQ4OTl9AAEAAAAAAKYlv4KfAmd_cznCubIXbyktYIo6_l9rnNjrS7IRrS3FBGGWOOHZcwdat6i1kGA4cVGuyknZ_qotPgC3i-M0kW2a47twCjfXrworxyTLTMDp \r\nBookmark your favorite jobs  and apply at your convenience.\r\n&#128176; Evaluate if your salary matches market standards \r\nhttps://click.my.jobs.ch/?qs=ABB7InYiOjEsImQiOjQ4OTl9AAEAAAAAAKYlv4KgPa334KXa8s-M7M-a_lfqnh02C5y4W9sQ1UjinWkZMjqMosrbHM_GbDp8nQS0zc51g56OIjT5qC0Gv3betqypTRAlBg3rnBo-oRHI \r\nwith our salary estimator. \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nAnd much more! So stay ahead and \r\nhttps://click.my.jobs.ch/?qs=ABB7InYiOjEsImQiOjQ4OTl9AAEAAAAAAKYlv4KhvOh1gTCGLF7-lrc9dqhmPPp2JBGr6deN_OW9CHp4Ptf-nk8UH5Azr3UHu2KE06uw8q6yduQzY-u80WvHKdGQSI3Sdq_8OwAogECu \r\nvisit us now &mdash;your next opportunity could be just a click away.\r\n\r\n\r\nYour jobup.ch Team\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nYou are registered with \r\nhttps://click.my.jobs.ch/?qs=ABB7InYiOjEsImQiOjQ4OTl9AAEAAAAAAKYlv4KiPhqKU2ZO7rM6P0owScx5N4YTuN2fuTO48oxB1CVvmdoycH-NLqidfrX5gR0Hyb4QNlLGKJ3ni0EpHYs2i8atTW_XKPlVmqTRaJFD \r\njobup.ch  as carlosedbaptista@gmail.com \r\n.\r\n\r\nhttps://click.my.jobs.ch/?qs=ABB7InYiOjEsImQiOjQ4OTl9AAEAAAAAAKYlv4KkFGf6LUa4W7oyF2xW9YhMZWhtAme7uZS0zgGpmLPElLj_4xoApaZKnRnWn96gdpwhcT7HrRz7QGH7aLZ6NXtahjZO2J8emsMW_sd6 \r\nUnsubscribe from this e-mail \r\n\r\n(Your profile on \r\nhttps://click.my.jobs.ch/?qs=ABB7InYiOjEsImQiOjQ4OTl9AAEAAAAAAKYlv4KlFSU4uBvF-q8rtaJoeKkFdCu93UtgvWS502Y-xSsYjWQqAk5Q-P7PMYE-XeONaglXWEg9wdN2Api5h58FGNChiXL5CB-DpZ8xlqXP \r\njobup.ch  will remain active)\r\n\r\n\r\nCopyright (c) 2026 | JobCloud SA, j\r\nhttps://click.my.jobs.ch/?qs=ABB7InYiOjEsImQiOjQ4OTl9AAEAAAAAAKYlv4KmGW7r1vRS-Q_QLd2eXTgu6jFXZi9a_5S5dOQl08mfu7H_s-kFgfOdklDk3L6lUQiKiQG0KX-jFqirmR5KSPbnaAxkFRxI3pUVh31H \r\nobup.ch ,\r\n\r\nRue Eugene Marziano 25, 1227 Les Acacias\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://click.my.jobs.ch/?qs=ABB7InYiOjEsImQiOjQ4OTl9AAEAAAAAAKYlv4Kn1gwGbvIkt04k7ZLfhbY3gAKNph-_oLciVi3qyQiY4-D70RdM0nQrvLZ4ynQhZm7IxGewnN6-VndNHOMgyHgZOkjOeR78Vvw0ZGwc \r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n \r\n\r\n"
